        "text": "I am therefore sending you a duplicate list of persons we have contacted\nand would appreciate your checking these for the above reasons. This is\npurely a request for information, as I have no concrete facts for or against\nthem in any way. I realize your work is primarily with other governmental\nbureaus, however the importance of this subject would tend to place it out\nof the usual run of civilian matters."
      },
